Here is a JavaScript program to calculate the factorial of a number:

```javascript
// JavaScript program to find factorial of a number
let num = 5;
let factorial = 1;
if (num < 0) {
    console.log('Factorial does not exist for negative numbers');
} else if (num === 0) {
    console.log('Factorial of 0 is 1');
} else {
    for (let i = 1; i <= num; i++) {
        factorial *= i;
    }
    console.log('Factorial:', factorial);
}
```

